strings: <voice_0x01001501><se_low>*: G'day? So what's goin' down up top then?
<voice_0x01001502><se_low>*: I'm goin' troppo stuck down this hole lookin' at these filthy cons all day.
<voice_0x01001503><se_low>*: I gotta tell ya, mate, there's some big news! The whole world's gone crazy!

<voice_0x01001504><se_low>*: Come on then, spit it out!
Don't make me guess, mate!

<voice_0x01001505><se_low>*: Okay, but it's gonna shock you! The Lord High Priest...went an' kicked the flamin' bucket
a month ago. An' that's fair dinkum, mate!

<voice_0x01001506><se_low>High Priest Rolo: What!? His Holiness is dead...
Th-That can't be!

<voice_0x01001507><se_low>*: Shut yer trap!
Don't forget where you are!

<voice_0x01001508><se_low>High Priest Rolo: B-But what happened!?
How did he die?

<voice_0x01001509><se_low>*: Didn't he just tell you to shut it,
ya big galah!?
<voice_0x0100150B><se_low>High Priest Rolo: It can't be...
<voice_0x0100150C><se_low>High Priest Rolo: How could this have happened? A month ago!? His Holiness has been dead all that time!
<voice_0x0100150D><se_low>High Priest Rolo: A whole month...

<voice_0x0100150E><se_low>High Priest Rolo: It must have been just after we were
brought here.
<voice_0x0100150F><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Listen to me, <hero>...
<voice_0x01001510><se_low>High Priest Rolo: When I overheard the guards talking about the Lord High Priest's death, do you know who sprung to mind?
<voice_0x01001511><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Marcello! He had something to do with this!

<voice_0x01001512><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Maybe he...! No! He may be a traitor,
but surely he wouldn't go that far?
<voice_0x01001513><se_low>High Priest Rolo: We're helpless to do anything while we're trapped here on Purgatory Island.
<voice_0x01001514><se_low>High Priest Rolo: We have to escape from this place if we're to find out the truth. There must be a way...

<voice_0x01001515><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Ah! I have an idea!
Gather everyone together and I'll tell you.
